content.webTitle: Football: Revised FA Cup fifth-round draw

fields.headline: Revised FA Cup fifth-round draw
fields.bodyText: The FA Cup fifth round draw is as follows: Man United v Man City Tranmere v Swansea Telford or Millwall v Burnley Sunderland v Birmingham Fulham v West Ham Arsenal v Chelsea Liverpool v Portsmouth Sheffield United v Colchester Ties to be played on February 14&15
